# AdGuard Home + Cloudflare (Hybrid DNS Setup)

## Environment Variables

Rename `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in your values:

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `CF_API_TOKEN` | Your Cloudflare API token |
| `SSL_EMAIL` | Email for Let's Encrypt |
| `DOMAIN_1` | Primary domain |
| `DOMAIN_2` | Secondary domain (optional) |
| `TZ` | Timezone (e.g., Asia/Kuala_Lumpur) |

```bash
CF_API_TOKEN=your_cloudflare_token_here
SSL_EMAIL=your_email@example.com
DOMAIN_1=dns.yourdomain.com
DOMAIN_2=yourdomain.com
TZ=Asia/Kuala_Lumpur
```